15/May/25 21:46;astefanov;Request was added to OPS-224886 to confirm database maintenance executes successfully, and additionally to fully reindex the database on the weekend (based on the time that takes, some additional coordination with Product and the client may be needed).

Separately, per Chen, there is an active discussion to archive data from the HMI database - currently at 20+ years - and leave only last 7 years. This will require additional work and testing, so it's not a confirmed decision yet.

Either one of those should address performance issues. Closing this ticket. Future performance issues may result in new ESC tickets and we'll follow up on the progress on OPS-224886.;;;
